content: nautilus 1954 is a washington-based & growing community of knitters and crocheters that have taken the mission to express gratitude and love to our united states navy submarine fleet through handknit & crocheted wool hats find us on facebook nautilus1954 & instagram @nautilus_1954 email woolhats@nautilus1954 com for more information and join our ravelry group nautilus 1954 /groups/nautilus-1954 enjoy our free pattern
